          }¨⍵       ⍝ ⍵: [ stack1a stack1b ... stack1z ] [stack2a stack2b ...]
      }

    ⍝ postprocessCleanup:   noOpts=1|0 ∇ string
    ⍝    Performs "final" cleanup and check of options etc.
      postprocessCleanup←{
